sp {get-digit1*propose*compute-result
   (state <s> ^name get-digit1
              ^digit1 <a1>
              ^digit2 <a2>
             -^result)
-->
   (<s> ^operator <op> + =)
   (<op> ^name compute-result)
}

### Add in the carry for multiplication

sp {get-digit1*apply*compute-result*addition
   (state <s> ^name get-digit1
              ^operator.name compute-result
              ^arithmetic.facts <af>
              ^arithmetic-problem.operation multiplication
              ^digit1 <a1>
              ^digit2 <a2>)
   (<af> ^digit1 <a1>
         ^digit2 <a2>
         ^sum <result>
         ^carry-borrow <carry-borrow>)
-->
   (<s> ^result <result>
        ^carry-borrow <carry-borrow>)
}

### Add in the carry for addition will be done by process-column*apply*compute-result*addition
### Subtract the borrow will be done by process-column*apply*compute-result*subtraction
